@startuml

title Weather Monitoring System State Transition Diagram

initial : Start

state "Initial" as Initial
state "Registered User" as RegisteredUser
state "Logged In" as LoggedIn
state "Location Invalid" as LocationInvalid
state "Weather Check" as WeatherCheck
state "Session Ended" as SessionEnded

Initial --> Register : Create Account
Register --> Login : Log In
Login --> LoggedIn : Successful Login
LoggedIn --> WeatherCheck : Check Weather
WeatherCheck --> ValidLocation : Location is Valid
ValidLocation --> WeatherDetails : View Details
WeatherDetails --> SessionEnded : Logout
WeatherCheck --> LocationInvalid : Invalid Location

@enduml
